abstract: "Research code, benchmark data, and experimental artifacts for PlanSafeBench-EVM, a semantic-policy validation benchmark and framework for pre-signing safety checks of AI-generated EVM transaction plans. The package includes the corrected v5.6 benchmark, LLM audit results, harmonized counterfactual robustness results, statistical hardening outputs, and public expert-validation v0.4 summary artifacts."

keywords:
  - AI safety
  - blockchain security
  - EVM
  - semantic-policy validation
  - transaction signing
  - smart contract security
  - expert validation
  - counterfactual robustness
  - reproducible research

